=== Search files ===

* search word Word in file

<pre>grep word file</pre>

* search word Word in file and print line numbers

<pre>grep -n word file</pre>

* search word Word in file and print only the names of files with a match

<pre>grep -l word file</pre>

* search word Word in file and print only the names of files without a match

<pre>grep -L word file</pre>

* search regular expression in a file

<pre>grep -e '.*' file</pre>
